data.description: Seller is offering 3% towards buyer's closing costs and/or to buy down a buyer's interest rate! Opportunity to own within the sought after community of Marley Park! Beautiful home built in 2020 with all of the right upgrades including a teen room and a lush entertainer's backyard! Home features an open layout with a gourmet kitchen that boasts white cabinets, black granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, pendant lights, chandelier in the dining room, and massive walk-in shower in the primary bathroom. Perfect for entertaining and everyday living! Home is within walking distance to the beautiful Clubhouse, firepit, resort style community pool, basketball court, cornhole station, horseshoe station, grill area, dog parks, and 8 themed community parks with playgrounds! Home is also minutes away from Prasada Shopping Center, restaurants, and entertainment shopping in the Surprise shopping center AND the newly built Village at Prasada shopping center, and AMC movie Theater! Home is located in the HEART of Surprise - the location and beauty of the home is unmatched!
